name: Night of Vespers
description: The upcoming Night of Vespers campaign was inspired by Thomas De Quincy’s Suspiria De Profundis, Giallo cinema, Dario Argento’s Le Tri Madri film trilogy, and Miskatonic River Press’s Our Ladies of Sorrow Call of Cthulhu campaign by Kevin Ross. The investigator expansion containins 5 investigators and 126 unique player cards, including 13 Specialist cards.
info: Campaign coming soon. Investigator expansion is finished and print-ready.
